description:
Food Court Wars - Season 2, Episode 2




Fat Shallot vs. Glutton Force 5

Two teams made up of Chicago food truck owners look forward to the stability that a food court location in West Dundee, Ill., can provide. Will married couple Sam and Sarah's Fat Shallot or best friends Pat and Tim's Glutton Force 5 win the coveted prize?




Original Air Date: 02-Mar-2014
